OL,3,CThree males arrested in relation to
OL,4,Cfatal Edenderry fire released without
OL,5,Ccharge
OL,7,FTwo men and a teenage boy arrested as
OL,8,Fpart of an investigation into the
OL,9,Ffatal house fire in Co Offaly, in
OL,10,Fwhich a woman and child died, have
OL,11,Fbeen released without charge.
OL,13,FFour-year-old Tadgh Farrell and his
OL,14,Fgreat-aunt, Mary Holt, 60, were killed
OL,15,Fin the blaze at Castleview Park,
OL,16,FEdenderry, on December 6.
OL,18,FGardai arrested three men on Tuesday
OL,19,Fin relation to the investigation: two
OL,20,Faged in their 20s and one in his 30s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
