OL,3,CThree males arrested in relation to
OL,4,Cfatal Edenderry fire released without
OL,5,Ccharge
OL,7,FLater that evening, they said they had
OL,8,Falso arrested a teenage boy.
OL,10,FOn Thursday morning, they said the
OL,11,Ffifth arrest ` of a man aged in his
OL,12,F20s ` occurred on Wednesday evening.
OL,14,FOn Saturday evening, the teenage boy
OL,15,Fand two men, one aged in his 20s and
OL,16,Fanother in his 30s, were released
OL,17,Fwithout charge.
OL,19,FA file is to be prepared for the
OL,20,FOffice of the Director of Public
OL,21,FProsecutions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
