OL,3,CThree males arrested in relation to
OL,4,Cfatal Edenderry fire released without
OL,5,Ccharge
OL,7,FA man aged in his 20s arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with the investigation
OL,9,Fremains in custody at a Garda station
OL,10,Funder Section 50 of the Criminal
OL,11,FJustice Act 2007.
OL,13,FOn Friday, Michael Dunne, aged 22 with
OL,14,Fan address in Co Kildare, appeared
OL,15,Fbefore Tullamore District Court
OL,16,Fcharged with criminal damage by arson
OL,17,Fand endangerment in relation to the
OL,18,Fcase.
